                           <item>
                              <abbr>መዝሙ፡</abbr> for <expan>መዝሙር፡ </expan> (e.g., <locus target="#27ra">27ra</locus>)</item>
                           <item>
                              <abbr>ፍ፡</abbr> for <expan>ፍትሕተ፡ ወንጽሕተ፡ ረስያ፡ ለዛቲ፡ ነፍስ፡ </expan> (e.g.,
