                           of the quires, close to the head and the tail of the codex.</decoNote>
                        <decoNote xml:id="b5">Blind tooled ornament on the leather cover (at least 8
                           tools were used: triple line fillet, cross hatching, double sine wave,
                           interlaced dot fillet, double circle, double crescent with eye,
                           corni-form, interlaced line fillet).</decoNote>
                     </binding>
